title: The Orchard Assault Mtn Bike Race
Blue Hills Classic
description: The Blue Hills Classic road race will be held Sunday May 4th, 2008 in the Blue Hills Reservation in Milton Massachusetts.  Race proceeds to benefit the Conservation Trust and Milton Rotary Scholarship Fund.
course: The course is a rolling 7 mile loop around Great Blue Hill.  Racers will proceed clockwise around the course, so all right hand turns.  Good road surface.  The course will utilize rolling closures at intersections.  Yellow line rule will be in effect.  Hill top finish.
notes: One day and annual license will be available at registration.  Camera at finish.  Results will be posted following each race at the registration area.  All USCF rules apply.
directions:
From Rte. 128:
-Take exit 2 Route 138 North (Milton)
-At first lights take a right (Blue River Road)
-Straight at sign (follow signs to registration)
-Take a right into Houghton\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\'s Pond parking area
